--
-- Challenge Mission - Late Siege
--
-- The player must destroy the enemy Capital and Landmarks to complete this challenge.
-- Success is measured by the time elapsed when both the Capital and Landmark are destroyed.
--
-- (c) Relic Entertainment 2020
--
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

